  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the project is to validate the use of Pain Monitor™ device, not invasive and
      simple of employment, for old people able to answer to a digital scale of pain intensity.

      The main objective is to develop and to validate a model of prediction of the pain in old
      subject at the time of the care, using the measure of variation of the skin conductance.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
